<p>
OMG can use audio samples from anywhere on the Internet. You can:
</p>

<ul>
   <li>Use URLs from your own website</li>
   <li>Use a file-sharing site with public URLs</li>
   <li>Upload directly to OMG</li>
</ul>

<p>Every user automatically gets <b>2 mb</b> of storage on OMG.</p>

<p>That doesn't sound like much, but for short MP3 samples like a a snare drum, it's more than it seems.</p>

